      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. This unit is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential for precise torque vectoring. The vehicle features a reinforced rear subframe\u2014a critical preventive measure\u2014along with a recently overhauled cooling system and a documented valve adjustment. Suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup delivers telepathic handling. While the exterior shows minor road wear, the mechanical vitals are strong, with the dual-VANOS system operating flawlessly and the engine pulling hard through the entire power band.",
